.@DuncanCastles: &ldquo;Liverpool are working on a deal. That is Sven Botman, in his first season at Lille from Ajax for an initial &euro;8m [&pound;7m]. He's been outstanding at Lille. Netherlands squad, 21 next month. Tall, quick, incredibly strong one-on-one.&quot; #awlfc [transfer window podcast]<br />
<br />
.@DuncanCastles: &quot;They would be willing to sell the player for twice and a little bit more than the fee they paid. They have been speaking to Botman&rsquo;s agent. Botman&rsquo;s agent likes the sounds of the conversations and believes there is a strong possibility of a January bid.&rdquo;

